---
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center">
      <span class="section-label">How It Works</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">No new software. No learning curve. Seriously.</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        SmolOps doesn't replace your software. It handles the work between your tools.
        Our AI agents plug into the channels and apps you already use every day.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#124923" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/>
            <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>You work like you always do</h3>
        <p>Send an email, forward an invoice, text a photo of your stockroom, or just go about your day. SmolOps works in the background.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step-arrow">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#9b8826" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#124923" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="2" fill="#124923" stroke="none"/>
            <path d="M8 13a4 4 0 0 1 8 0" fill="none"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>AI handles the admin</h3>
        <p>Our agents read emails, organize data, prepare documents, follow up with customers, and handle the repetitive tasks that eat your evenings.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step-arrow">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#9b8826" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#124923" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/>
            <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>You get results, not homework</h3>
        <p>A ready-to-send vendor order. A qualified lead list. A weekly business summary. Delivered to your inbox. Review, approve, done.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="channels">
      <p class="channels-label">Works with the tools you already use:</p>
      <div class="channel-list">
        <div class="channel">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#72641c" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          <span>Email</span>
        </div>
        <div class="channel">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#72641c" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
          <span>Text / SMS</span>
        </div>
        <div class="channel">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#72641c" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M23 19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4"/></svg>
          <span>Photo Upload</span>
        </div>
        <div class="channel">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#72641c" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
          <span>Cloud Storage</span>
        </div>
        <div class="channel">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#72641c" stroke-width="1.8"><rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/></svg>
          <span>Phone Call</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="positioning-line">
      <p>If you're spending nights catching up on emails, paperwork, and scheduling, SmolOps can probably automate it.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-it-works {
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .steps {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0;
    margin-top: 56px;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .step {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 300px;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .step-icon {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: var(--cream);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
  }

  .step h3 {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--green-dark);
  }

  .step p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .step-arrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding-top: 24px;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .channels {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .channels-label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--green-dark);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .channel-list {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 36px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .channel {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--olive);
  }

  .positioning-line {
    margin-top: 48px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .positioning-line p {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--green-dark);
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .steps {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .step-arrow {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
      padding-top: 0;
    }
    .channel-list {
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .channels {
      padding: 24px 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
